  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study the investigators are going to study the retinal nerve fibers layers (RNFL)
      modification of two groups of patients, one taking no drugs, the other taking forskolin,
      rutin and vitamins B1 and B2.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
